corpus: entire set of texts
represent documents as H = (H_1,...H_d)  # of occurance

N-gram model: model condiction on n-1 prev words
p(w_l | w_l-1 .... w_l -n+1) is a multinomial ususlli bi or tri gram otherwise too costy

Clustering model:
assume corpus is generated by a multinomial mixture model:
  pi(H) = sum c_j P(H | t_k)  P different topic called topic models.
